{"word":"G3403 - μιμνήσκω - mimnḗskō - mim-nace'-ko - Be mindful","slug":"G3403","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μιμνήσκω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>mimnḗskō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>mim-nace'-ko"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Be mindful"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03BC;&#x03B9;&#x03BC;&#x03BD;&#x03B7;&#x0301;&#x03C3;&#x03BA;&#x03C9; - mimne&#x0304;sko&#x0304;</b> - <i>mim-nace'-ko</i><p/>A prolonged form of <a href=\"#/G3415\">G3415</a> (from which some of the tenses are borrowed); to <i>remind</i>, that is, (middle voice) to <i>recall to mind:</i> - be mindful, remember."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G3417\">G3417</a>, <a href=\"#/G3418\">G3418</a>, <a href=\"#/G3419\">G3419</a>, <a href=\"#/G3420\">G3420</a>, <a href=\"#/G3421\">G3421</a>, <a href=\"#/G3422\">G3422</a>"}]}